{"tid":581862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點向八婆派帽ex追錢","createTime":"2018-03-05T16:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T13:15:38.000Z","uid":83789,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e910df15488b1074322d438f0c01ebb6148395e","tid":581862,"uid":83789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"(問朋友借ac 代po)<br />\n<br />\n各位爸打<br />\n同ex呢條八婆分左手一年<br />\n因為佢比帽我帶<br />\n果時好愛佢，當佢係我老婆咁錫<br />\n分手前佢屋企有事借左大約20萬比佢<br />\n但好多都係現金直接比<br />\n而家佢條撚樣唔還錢<br />\n我又無乜證據係身<br />\n請問有乜途徑可以追到錢<br />\n又或者我可以點做令佢承認借過我錢，以方便彩取法律行動？<br />\n以前係戇鳩，但唔撚想益條八婆，幾煩都唔緊要，最緊要可以煩鳩佢。"},{"pid":"4bbec6744e8fd4090ddf2e1c05a158c78764d4d0","tid":581862,"uid":30604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"呢個係憑佢本事借返黎既廿萬，點解要還？屌你老母！"},{"pid":"df3e874f4c22fd736b233fcd60c4df76d03363b3","tid":581862,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"比啲風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a156c20d26aae38c40ee17d48159c4c051e4fe","tid":581862,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:27:48.000Z","msg":"叫佢肉償"},{"pid":"630fcc225f935fe053db6c96f8c13a336328e497","tid":581862,"uid":83789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3e874f4c22fd736b233fcd60c4df76d03363b3","tid":581862,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"比啲風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"當時講明係借，唔係比佢。 同埋而家佢態度愈來愈惡劣我先會咁嬲！"},{"pid":"91d900c6016fc959be56d2994c9ca1e1cf40994a","tid":581862,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"630fcc225f935fe053db6c96f8c13a336328e497","tid":581862,"uid":83789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3e874f4c22fd736b233fcd60c4df76d03363b3","tid":581862,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":